SOME PEOPLE WOULD CALL WHAT IS

00:11:02.430 --> 00:11:03.500
CENTRAL TO HIS OR HER RELIGIOUS

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:04.400
PRACTICE PRAYING.

00:11:04.400 --> 00:11:06.400
DO YOU FIND THE SAME KINDS

00:11:06.400 --> 00:11:07.200
OF BRAIN ACTIVITY DURING WHAT

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:08.660
SOME OTHER TRADITIONS WOULD CALL

00:11:08.660 --> 00:11:09.500
PRAYING OR PRAYING DEEPLY

00:11:09.500 --> 00:11:10.830
OR PRAYING FOR A LONG TIME

00:11:10.830 --> 00:11:11.630
OR PRAYING FULLY?

00:11:11.630 --> 00:11:13.630
ABSOLUTELY.

