EVEN WHEN PEOPLE PRAY THEY HAVE

00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:16.000
A SENSE OF CONNECTING

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:16.900
WITH SOMETHING GREATER THAN

00:11:16.900 --> 00:11:18.260
THEMSELVES.

00:11:18.260 --> 00:11:20.100
Reporter: NOW THAT YOU HAVE

00:11:20.100 --> 00:11:22.160
BEEN ABLE TO MAP WHAT IS GOING

00:11:22.160 --> 00:11:23.560
ON IN THE BRAIN WHILE PEOPLE ARE

00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:24.530
HAVING CERTAIN KINDS

