OF EXPERIENCES, WHEN PEOPLE ARE

00:11:25.660 --> 00:11:27.100
HAVING DEEPLY MEDITATIVE

00:11:27.100 --> 00:11:28.060
OR PRAYERFUL EXPERIENCES, WHAT

00:11:28.060 --> 00:11:29.560
ELSE WOULD YOU LIKE TO KNOW?

00:11:29.560 --> 00:11:30.830
WELL, ONE OF THE THINGS THAT

00:11:30.830 --> 00:11:33.300
WE'RE VERY INTERESTED IN IS

00:11:33.300 --> 00:11:34.430
SEEING THE LINK BETWEEN WHAT

00:11:34.430 --> 00:11:35.500
HAPPENS DURING SPIRITUAL

00:11:35.500 --> 00:11:36.700
PRACTICES AND EXPERIENCES

00:11:36.700 --> 00:11:37.630
TO PSYCHOLOGICAL AND PHYSICAL

00:11:37.630 --> 00:11:38.660
HEALTH.

00:11:38.660 --> 00:11:41.430
SO THAT WE CAN SEE EXACTLY WHY,

00:11:41.430 --> 00:11:42.500
WHEN PEOPLE PRAY OR MEDITATE,

00:11:42.500 --> 00:11:43.600
WHY THEY LOWER THEIR BLOOD

00:11:43.600 --> 00:11:44.700
PRESSURE, WHY THEY MAY AFFECT

00:11:44.700 --> 00:11:45.960
THEIR IMMUNE SYSTEM

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:48.530
OR THEIR HORMONE SYSTEM, ALL

00:11:48.530 --> 00:11:49.760
CHANGES THAT HAVE BEEN SHOWN

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:50.900
TO OCCUR BUT PEOPLE DON'T

00:11:50.900 --> 00:11:51.800
UNDERSTAND EXACTLY WHY THAT'S

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:52.730
HAPPENING.

00:11:52.730 --> 00:11:54.560
Reporter: THERE ARE SOME WHO

00:11:54.560 --> 00:11:57.330
MIGHT ARGUE THAT ULTIMATELY

00:11:57.330 --> 00:11:59.030
TRYING TO SORT OF FIND WAYS

00:11:59.030 --> 00:12:02.660
TO KIND OF REPLICATE

00:12:02.660 --> 00:12:04.160
THE HEALTHFUL OR BENEFICIAL

00:12:04.160 --> 00:12:05.900
EFFECTS OF THE RELIGIOUS

00:12:05.900 --> 00:12:06.860
EXPERIENCE SO THAT IT CAN BE

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:10.630
DISPENSED.

00:12:10.630 --> 00:12:12.030
WHICH IS NOT WHAT RELIGION IS

00:12:12.030 --> 00:12:12.330
FOR.

00:12:12.330 --> 00:12:13.630
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

00:12:13.630 --> 00:12:14.800
AND WE ACTUALLY REALLY DO NOT

00:12:14.800 --> 00:12:16.300
FEEL THAT THE WAY OF SOME

00:12:16.300 --> 00:12:17.360
OF OUR COLLEAGUES, WHICH IS THAT

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:19.000
THERE ARE WAYS OF STIMULATING

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:20.160
THESE KINDS OF EXPERIENCES THAT

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:21.800
YOU MAY ULTIMATELY BE ABLE TO DO

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:23.600
SOMETHING WHERE PEOPLE WOULD

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.630
COME IN AND YOU'D STIMULATE

00:12:24.630 --> 00:12:25.730
A PARTICULAR RELIGIOUS

00:12:25.730 --> 00:12:26.700
EXPERIENCE AND THEN SEND THEM

00:12:26.700 --> 00:12:27.730
OUT.

00:12:27.730 --> 00:12:28.960
I DON'T THINK OUR RESEARCH

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:30.960
SUGGESTS THAT.

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:33.100
IN FACT, WHAT I THINK IT SHOWS

00:12:33.100 --> 00:12:34.060
IS THAT THESE ARE VERY COMPLEX

00:12:34.060 --> 00:12:35.900
KIND OF EXPERIENCES.

00:12:35.900 --> 00:12:37.600
SOMETHING THAT IS FAR DEEPER

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:38.530
THAN WHAT SOMEBODY COULD JUST

00:12:38.530 --> 00:12:39.460
STIMULATE THROUGH ELECTRODES

00:12:39.460 --> 00:12:40.700
OR THROUGH SOME TYPE OF DRUG

00:12:40.700 --> 00:12:41.630
EXPERIENCE OR SOMETHING LIKE

00:12:41.630 --> 00:12:43.730
THAT.

00:12:43.730 --> 00:12:45.260
Reporter: AND YET,

00:12:45.260 --> 00:12:46.830
WITHOUT ELECTRODES OR DRUGS,

00:12:46.830 --> 00:12:49.030
THAT IS EXACTLY WHAT

00:12:49.030 --> 00:12:51.030
DR. MICHAEL BAIME IS DISPENSING.

00:12:51.030 --> 00:12:52.500
AND OVER THE LAST EIGHT YEARS

00:12:52.500 --> 00:12:55.660
WE'VE TRAINED MORE THAN

00:12:55.660 --> 00:12:56.960
1,300 PEOPLE TO PRACTICE THESE

00:12:56.960 --> 00:13:00.230
ANCIENT TECHNIQUES.

00:13:00.230 --> 00:13:00.960
AND I JUST KNOW THAT IT MAKES

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:01.960
A DIFFERENCE.

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:02.860
I DON'T NEED A BRAIN SCAN

00:13:02.860 --> 00:13:04.800
TO TELL ME THAT THESE TWO PEOPLE

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:06.060
ARE HEALTHIER, THAT THEY FEEL

00:13:06.060 --> 00:13:06.960
BETTER, THAT THEY FUNCTION

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:08.800
BETTER IN THEIR LIVES.

00:13:08.800 --> 00:13:11.430
THEY TELL US AND WE HAVE

00:13:11.430 --> 00:13:13.030
STUDIES, RESEARCH THAT SHOWS

00:13:13.030 --> 00:13:16.800
THAT THAT'S THE CASE.

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:18.100
Reporter: YOU'RE MAPPING

00:13:18.100 --> 00:13:19.160
THE WAY THE BRAIN BEHAVES

00:13:19.160 --> 00:13:20.060
DURING A CERTAIN KIND

00:13:20.060 --> 00:13:22.230
OF SPIRITUAL EXPERIENCE.

00:13:22.230 --> 00:13:24.130
ISN'T THE INESCAPABLE CONCLUSION

00:13:24.130 --> 00:13:25.800
THAT THOSE SPIRITUAL EXPERIENCES

00:13:25.800 --> 00:13:27.060
ARE A FUNCTION OF THE BRAIN'S

00:13:27.060 --> 00:13:29.460
ACTIVITY, THAT THE BRAIN IS

00:13:29.460 --> 00:13:30.460
DOING THIS RATHER THAN GOD DOING

00:13:30.460 --> 00:13:31.400
THIS?

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:33.060
SOMEBODY WHO IS VERY

00:13:33.060 --> 00:13:34.560
RELIGIOUS MIGHT LOOK AT THIS

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:35.360
AND SAY, "YOU KNOW, OF COURSE

00:13:35.360 --> 00:13:36.300
THIS MAKES SENSE.

00:13:36.300 --> 00:13:36.960
IF GOD IS UP THERE AND WE'RE

00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:37.500
GOING HAVE SOME KIND

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:38.200
OF COMMUNICATION OR SOME KIND

00:13:38.200 --> 00:13:38.900
OF CONTACT AND SOME KNOWLEDGE

00:13:38.900 --> 00:13:40.700
OF GOD, THEN OUR BRAINS

00:13:40.700 --> 00:13:42.160
NECESSARILY WOULD BE DESIGNED

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:45.760
BY GOD, PERHAPS, TO HAVE THAT

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:46.900
ABILITY, TO HAVE THAT

00:13:46.900 --> 00:13:48.200
EXPERIENCE, TO HAVE THAT SENSE

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.160
OF COMMUNICATION OR UNION

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.530
WITH GOD."

00:13:50.530 --> 00:13:51.860
Reporter: WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:13:51.860 --> 00:13:53.100
WELL, I THINK THE ANSWER

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:55.060
ACTUALLY LIES SOMEWHERE

00:13:55.060 --> 00:13:57.630
IN BETWEEN, AND I THINK THAT

00:13:57.630 --> 00:13:58.900
WE CAN'T REALLY GET AT THE TRUE

00:13:58.900 --> 00:14:00.630
ANSWERS ABOUT WHAT IS OUT THERE

00:14:00.630 --> 00:14:02.200
IN REALITY WITHOUT LOOKING

00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:03.200
AT BOTH THE SCIENTIFIC AS WELL

00:14:03.200 --> 00:14:04.900
AS THE SPIRITUAL PERSPECTIVE.

00:14:04.900 --> 00:14:06.800
AND WHETHER THAT ULTIMATE

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:08.760
REALITY BECOMES JUST PHYSICAL,

00:14:08.760 --> 00:14:10.000
MATERIAL REALITY, OR SOMETHING

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:12.860
THAT IS VERY SPIRITUAL

00:14:12.860 --> 00:14:14.400
AND DIVINE IN ITS ORIENTATION,

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:16.760
THOSE ARE THE QUESTIONS THAT WE,

00:14:16.760 --> 00:14:18.030
THAT ALL HUMAN BEINGS ULTIMATELY

00:14:18.030 --> 00:14:19.500
HAVE TO FACE AND COME TO TERMS

00:14:19.500 --> 00:14:20.500
WITH.

00:14:20.500 --> 00:14:21.900
Reporter: FOR MICHAEL BAIME,

00:14:21.900 --> 00:14:24.360
HOWEVER, THERE MAY NEVER BE

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:25.460
A COMING TO TERMS WHEN IT COMES

00:14:25.460 --> 00:14:27.000
TO SPIRITUALITY AND THE BRAIN.

00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:29.900
WHETHER WE CALL IT GOD

00:14:29.900 --> 00:14:34.260
OR SOMETHING ULTIMATE

00:14:34.260 --> 00:14:36.260
AND ABSOLUTE, THE NATURE

00:14:36.260 --> 00:14:38.330
OF REALITY, THE FUNDAMENTAL

00:14:38.330 --> 00:14:39.760
NATURE, IT'S HARD TO GET AROUND

00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:41.330
SOME KIND OF LABEL.

00:14:41.330 --> 00:14:43.660
YOU COULD CALL IT EMPTINESS,

00:14:43.660 --> 00:14:45.530
AS SOME SCHOOLS OF BUDDHISM DO.

00:14:45.530 --> 00:14:46.600
BUT YOU'RE STILL JUST APPLYING

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:47.900
A LABEL THAT MEANS SOMETHING

00:14:47.900 --> 00:14:49.500
ABSOLUTE.

00:14:49.500 --> 00:14:50.430
THAT'S HOW OUR VOCABULARIES

00:14:50.430 --> 00:14:51.400
WORK.

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:52.560
WE CAN ONLY TALK ABOUT THINGS

00:14:52.560 --> 00:14:53.300
THAT CAN BE DESCRIBED IN WORDS.

00:14:53.300 --> 00:14:54.030
I THINK THAT THIS EXPERIENCE IS

00:14:54.030 --> 00:14:55.900
BIGGER THAN THE KINDS OF THING

00:14:55.900 --> 00:15:00.360
THAT CAN BE ENCOMPASSED

00:15:00.360 --> 00:15:15.500
BY VOCABULARY.

00:15:15.500 --> 00:15:16.830
Reporter: STREETS FILLED

00:15:16.830 --> 00:15:18.230
WITH THE FACES OF THOSE LOST

00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:21.630
ON SEPTEMBER 11th.

00:15:21.630 --> 00:15:22.400
MEMORIES MINGLING WITH DISBELIEF

00:15:22.400 --> 00:15:23.900
THAT THE THOUSANDS WHO DIED ARE,

00:15:23.900 --> 00:15:33.300
IN FACT, GONE.

00:15:33.300 --> 00:15:35.160
THERE'S STILL, FOR MANY, THAT

00:15:35.160 --> 00:15:37.630
SPIRITUAL SENSE OF CONNECTION

00:15:37.630 --> 00:15:39.600
TO THOSE WHO HAVE PASSED AWAY.

00:15:39.600 --> 00:15:40.900
AND FOR SOME SCIENTISTS, WHAT

00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:42.360
HAPPENS IN THE BRAIN TO SUSTAIN

00:15:42.360 --> 00:15:43.960
THAT CONNECTION MAY BE ANOTHER

00:15:43.960 --> 00:15:48.430
PATHWAY TO GOD.

00:15:48.430 --> 00:15:49.560
SOME OF THE RELATIVES OF THOSE

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:51.030
WHO DIED ATTENDED A TAPING

00:15:51.030 --> 00:15:52.100
OF "CROSSING OVER

00:15:52.100 --> 00:15:54.260
WITH JOHN EDWARD."

00:15:54.260 --> 00:15:55.860
EDWARD IS A MEDIUM WHO CLAIMS

00:15:55.860 --> 00:15:56.760
HE CAN CONTACT LOVED ONES WHO

00:15:56.760 --> 00:16:01.600
HAVE DIED.

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:03.000
THE IMPORTANT THING YOU

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:04.530
CONTINUE TO CONNECT WITH OTHERS

00:16:04.530 --> 00:16:08.100
DURING YOUR PROCESS OF GRIEVING.

00:16:08.100 --> 00:16:09.330
Reporter: THIS IS A SHOW

00:16:09.330 --> 00:16:14.560
FROM LAST AUGUST.

00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:15.300
SHOWS WITH THE 9/11. NEXT OF KIN

00:16:15.300 --> 00:16:15.860
WERE NEVER AIRED.

00:16:15.860 --> 00:16:16.600
CRITICS ACCUSED EDWARD OF TAKING

00:16:16.600 --> 00:16:17.300
ADVANTAGE OF THEIR SUFFERING.

00:16:17.300 --> 00:16:18.030
PEOPLE ASK US, THEY SAY, "ARE

00:16:18.030 --> 00:16:18.760
YOU TRYING TO PROVE SURVIVAL

00:16:18.760 --> 00:16:19.830
OF CONSCIOUSNESS?"

00:16:19.830 --> 00:16:20.630
AND WE SAY ABSOLUTELY NO.

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:21.400
WHAT WE'RE TRYING TO DO IS

00:16:21.400 --> 00:16:22.160
ENCOURAGE RESEARCH ON SURVIVAL

00:16:22.160 --> 00:16:23.160
OF CONSCIOUSNESS.

00:16:23.160 --> 00:16:23.960
AND IN FACT, WE'RE TRYING

00:16:23.960 --> 00:16:24.800
TO GIVE SURVIVAL OF

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:25.960
CONSCIOUSNESS THE OPPORTUNITY

00:16:25.960 --> 00:16:27.300
TO PROVE ITSELF OR NOT.

00:16:27.300 --> 00:16:28.530
Reporter: MEDIUMS, INCLUDING

00:16:28.530 --> 00:16:30.330
JOHN EDWARD, THOUGH, HAVE

00:16:30.330 --> 00:16:31.360
SUBMITTED THEMSELVES

00:16:31.360 --> 00:16:32.260
TO SCIENTIFIC SCRUTINY

00:16:32.260 --> 00:16:33.800
AS ADMINISTERED BY THE HEAD

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:35.800
OF THE UNIVERSITY OF ARIZONA'S

00:16:35.800 --> 00:16:37.000
HUMAN ENERGY SYSTEMS LABORATORY

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:38.560
PROFESSOR GARY SCHWARTZ.

00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:40.730
THE MEDIUMS WHO PARTICIPATE

00:16:40.730 --> 00:16:41.530
IN THIS RESEARCH HAVE TO WORK

00:16:41.530 --> 00:16:42.900
UNDER VERY UNUSUAL

00:16:42.900 --> 00:16:45.660
AND CONTROLLED CONDITIONS

00:16:45.660 --> 00:16:47.530
Reporter: TO PREVENT ANY

00:16:47.530 --> 00:16:48.560
TRICKERY, SCHWARTZ HAD MEDIUMS

00:16:48.560 --> 00:16:50.530
HIDDEN BEHIND A SCREEN

00:16:50.530 --> 00:16:52.030
FROM THE PERSON THEY WERE TRYING

00:16:52.030 --> 00:16:53.630
TO HELP CONTACT DEAD RELATIVES.

00:16:53.630 --> 00:16:54.600
A PERSON THEY HAD NEVER MET

00:16:54.600 --> 00:17:00.460
BEFORE.

00:17:00.460 --> 00:17:01.900
IN ADDITION, THOSE WHO THE

00:17:01.900 --> 00:17:02.830
MEDIUMS

00:17:02.830 --> 00:17:03.600
WERE TRYING TO HELP COULD NOT

00:17:03.600 --> 00:17:04.330
SAY A WORD.

00:17:04.330 --> 00:17:05.700
AND WHAT WE'VE DISCOVERED,

00:17:05.700 --> 00:17:07.930
ACTUALLY QUITE TO MY SURPRISE,

00:17:07.930 --> 00:17:09.430
IS THAT THEY REALLY DO GET VERY

00:17:09.430 --> 00:17:10.260
ACCURATE INFORMATION THAT IS

00:17:10.260 --> 00:17:11.260
STRONGLY CONSISTENT

00:17:11.260 --> 00:17:12.200
WITH THE IDEA THAT PEOPLE'S

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:12.900
DEPARTED LOVED ONES ARE STILL

00:17:12.900 --> 00:17:14.300
HERE.

00:17:14.300 --> 00:17:15.800
Reporter: THAT IS, SCHWARTZ

00:17:15.800 --> 00:17:18.230
CONTENDS, SOME ENERGY OF THOSE

00:17:18.230 --> 00:17:19.960
WHO HAVE DIED CONTINUES TO EXIST

00:17:19.960 --> 00:17:21.130
IN SUCH A MANNER THAT FEW

00:17:21.130 --> 00:17:21.900
PEOPLE, THE MEDIUMS, CAN

00:17:21.900 --> 00:17:24.260
ACTUALLY DISCERN.

00:17:24.260 --> 00:17:26.600
AND, OF COURSE, WHAT

00:17:26.600 --> 00:17:28.330
OUR MEDIUMSHIP RESEARCH DOES IS

00:17:28.330 --> 00:17:29.660
IT FORCES US TO REALLY THINK

00:17:29.660 --> 00:17:31.660
THAT THE EARTH IS NOT FLAT BUT,

00:17:31.660 --> 00:17:33.900
IN FACT, IT'S ROUND.

00:17:33.900 --> 00:17:40.530
IT POINTS TO A NEW VISION, WHICH

00:17:40.530 --> 00:17:42.530
SAYS THAT MAYBE THERE REALLY IS

00:17:42.530 --> 00:17:43.430
SOMETHING MUCH BIGGER THAN US.

00:17:43.430 --> 00:17:45.030
AND WE HAVE THE CAPABILITY

00:17:45.030 --> 00:17:46.160
TO ACTUALLY APPRECIATE IT

00:17:46.160 --> 00:17:47.930
AND LEARN TO LIVE WITHIN IT,

00:17:47.930 --> 00:17:49.630
AND POSSIBLY MANIFEST IT.

00:17:49.630 --> 00:17:51.630
Reporter: SCHWARTZ LAB IS

00:17:51.630 --> 00:17:52.730
DEDICATED TO MEASURING THE LOW

00:17:52.730 --> 00:17:54.500
LEVELS OF ENERGY THAT COME

00:17:54.500 --> 00:17:56.130
FROM THE BODY AND WHAT THOSE

00:17:56.130 --> 00:17:57.360
ENERGY LEVELS CAN TELL US

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:58.660
ABOUT OUR PHYSICAL AND MENTAL

00:17:58.660 --> 00:17:59.600
HEALTH.

00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:01.160
AND WHETHER OR NOT THAT ENERGY,

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:02.530
INCLUDING OUR OWN CONSCIOUSNESS,

00:18:02.530 --> 00:18:04.560
SURVIVES DEATH.

00:18:04.560 --> 00:18:06.460
THE TRUTH IS, THOSE KINDS

00:18:06.460 --> 00:18:09.100
OF QUESTIONS, SUCH

00:18:09.100 --> 00:18:10.900
AS COMMUNICATION WITH DIVINITY,

00:18:10.900 --> 00:18:12.900
PEOPLE WHO LITERALLY TALK TO GOD

00:18:12.900 --> 00:18:14.930
ON A REGULAR BASIS, OR THE IDEA

00:18:14.930 --> 00:18:17.430
OF SENDING LOVING ENERGY

00:18:17.430 --> 00:18:19.000
TO PEOPLE THAT WE CARE ABOUT,

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:22.200
OR PRAYING FOR OTHERS,

00:18:22.200 --> 00:18:24.200
OR THE ALTRUISTIC

